      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1720161976,
      "updated": 1720175922
    },
    {
      "id": "66877f29b8bbfc00000abb71",
      "text": "\tいつも見てる体調バロメーターが狂うから服薬を渋っている",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1720155946,
      "updated": 1720155990
    },
    {
      "id": "668754537c8c6d0000ec34d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6171231417617a001d7c8c6d",
      "created": 1720144979,
      "updated": 1720144979
    },
    {
      "id": "668794a16eb40600008306e4",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1720161442,
      "updated": 1720161444
    },
    {
      "id": "668794a36eb40600008306e6",
      "text": "\t✂ [マンションの壁に蛾の蛹が大量発生している]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1720161444,
      "updated": 1777702939
    },
    {
      "id": "6687a9ff6eb4060000034701",
      "text": "\t暑すぎる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1720166913,
      "updated": 1720568747
    },
    {
      "id": "6687b3616eb4060000034702",
      "text": "\t明日の夜かな",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1720169315,
      "updated": 1720169345
    },
    {
      "id": "6687b3806eb4060000034703",
      "text": "\t\t[https://www.monogatari-series.com/oms/ 〈物語〉シリーズ オフ＆モンスターシーズン｜公式サイト]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1720169346,
      "updated": 1720169348
    },
    {
      "id": "66895d966eb406000093c479",
      "text": "\t\t見た。物語シリーズは、なんだかんだで追いかけられている気がする（覚えているかは怪しい）",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1720278423,
      "updated": 1720278461
    },
    {
      "id": "66879819c9ec6a000072cfe5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1720162329,
      "updated": 1720162330
    },
    {
      "id": "6687981ac9ec6a000072cfe6",
      "text": "[cak.icon]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1720162331,
      "updated": 1720162333
    },
    {
      "id": "6687981ec9ec6a000072cfe7",
      "text": " なんとなく「ねぇSiri…」と呼びかけたら答えてくれた",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1720162334,
      "updated": 1720162361
    },
    {
      "id": "66879839c9ec6a000072cfe8",
      "text": "  いつのまにheyじゃなくてもよくなったのだろう",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1720162361,
      "updated": 1720162380
    },
    {
      "id": "6687e42bc9ec6a000033df08",
      "text": " ゼンゼロに時間を吸われている",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1720181803,
      "updated": 1720181815
    },
    {
      "id": "668794a26eb40600008306e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1720161442,
      "updated": 1720161442
    },
    {
      "id": "66879f30aff09e0000d8aa22",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720164144,
      "updated": 1720164146
    },
    {
      "id": "66879f32aff09e0000d8aa23",
      "text": " すごくいいリアルGeoGuessrポイントがあった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720164147,
      "updated": 1720164167
    },
    {
      "id": "66879f46aff09e0000d8aa24",
      "text": " 　が写真は撮り損ねました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720164167,
      "updated": 1720164172
    },
    {
      "id": "66879f4daff09e0000d8aa25",
      "text": " 　口頭で説明すると、水面から赤い鳥居が立っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720164173,
      "updated": 1720164196
    },
    {
      "id": "66879f6daff09e0000d8aa26",
      "text": " 　なお広島にはいません",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720164210,
      "updated": 1720164212
    },
    {
      "id": "668b4574aff09e00001cb6d1",
      "text": " 　[https://gyazo.com/8544d77c989c7b2a8a7da3b1b0b9d620]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720403316,
      "updated": 1720403372
    },
    {
      "id": "668dcbb95e90c000000ad2e4",
      "text": " 　[弁天島]だ[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1720568761,
      "updated": 1720568771
    },
    {
      "id": "66879f74aff09e0000d8aa27",
      "text": "　今の瞬間、眠いのだが、この眠気を保存しといて夜に取り出せないかな()",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720164212,
      "updated": 1720164721
    },
    {
      "id": "6687a171aff09e0000d8aa2c",
      "text": "　　明日早起きなので…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720164721,
      "updated": 1720164734
    },
    {
      "id": "6687a296aff09e0000d8aa2d",
      "text": "　[自己家畜化]の本を読んでる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1720165015,
      "updated": 1720165651
    },
    {
      "id": "6687a2a4aff09e0000d8aa2e",
      "text": "　　「人間はどこまで家畜か」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720165043,
      "updated": 1720165043
    },
    {
      "id": "6687a2b1aff09e0000d8aa2f",
      "text": "　　暴力の人類史",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720165043,
      "updated": 1720165056
    },
    {
      "id": "6687a314aff09e0000d8aa30",
      "text": "　　[アナール学派]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1720165140,
      "updated": 1720173870
    },
    {
      "id": "6687a327aff09e0000d8aa31",
      "text": "　　　においの歴史　嗅覚と社会的想像力",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720165160,
      "updated": 1720165178
    },
    {
      "id": "6687a33aaff09e0000d8aa32",
      "text": "　　眠くなって全然読めなかったー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720165178,
      "updated": 1720167499
    },
    {
      "id": "6687ad24aff09e0000d8aa39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1720167716,
      "updated": 1720167716
    },
